Description: GMB BAR should  be Successful from USSD
GMB BAR should Not  be Successful from USSD when  user is already barred for GMB by the Reciever Msisdn
GMB BAR should Not  be Successful from USSD  when Mandatory Parameters are missing
GMB BAR should Not be Successful from USSD When MSISDN1 Length is not Between Specified SystemPreference MIN_MSISDN_LENGTH and MAX_MSISDN_LENGTH
GMB BAR should Not be Successful from USSD When MSISDN2 Length is not Between Specified SystemPreference MIN_MSISDN_LENGTH and MAX_MSISDN_LENGTH
